#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:BIM_Setup.svg|16px]] [[BIM_Setup|BIM Setup]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Manage → [[Image:BIM_Setup.svg|16px]] BIM Setup}} option from the menu.

